00:17:01.199 --> 00:17:03.030
'That Monday morning

00:17:03.040 --> 00:17:08.710
at about 7 a.m.,

00:17:08.720 --> 00:17:11.990
I went as I always did then. Now I

00:17:12.000 --> 00:17:14.069
come to the office before I go to the

00:17:14.079 --> 00:17:16.470
television studio to spend some time

00:17:16.480 --> 00:17:18.549
with the Lord. I do that every morning.

00:17:18.559 --> 00:17:21.510
Then I would get in my car and drive.

00:17:21.520 --> 00:17:23.510
There's a railroad track about a half

00:17:23.520 --> 00:17:26.069
mile from our house,

00:17:26.079 --> 00:17:28.069
and it was a place of

00:17:28.079 --> 00:17:30.470
privacy, and I would park there and

00:17:30.480 --> 00:17:34.789
read my Bible and then walk down that

00:17:34.799 --> 00:17:39.190
track praying, seeking the

00:17:39.190 --> 00:17:39.200
Lord.'That's

00:17:39.200 --> 00:17:41.350
what I would do

00:17:41.360 --> 00:17:44.630
every morning. And that morning, July

00:17:44.640 --> 00:17:48.630
the 1st, 1985,

00:17:48.640 --> 00:17:51.669
that Monday morning at about 7 a.m., as

00:17:51.679 --> 00:17:54.230
I studied the word of God for a period

00:17:54.240 --> 00:17:58.150
of time, and then got out and walked

00:17:58.160 --> 00:18:00.150
down the track,

00:18:00.160 --> 00:18:03.190
all of a sudden,

00:18:03.200 --> 00:18:05.750
all around me,

00:18:05.760 --> 00:18:10.310
as far as I could see, were fields of cotton.

00:18:10.320 --> 00:18:14.070
I was raised in northeast Louisiana

00:18:14.080 --> 00:18:16.230
and

00:18:16.240 --> 00:18:18.870
I know what cotton is.

00:18:18.880 --> 00:18:20.470
I have chopped cotton. I've picked

00:18:20.480 --> 00:18:24.390
cotton, so I know what it is.

00:18:24.400 --> 00:18:27.350
And as I saw these fields of cotton go

00:18:27.360 --> 00:18:30.789
over the horizon in every direction,

00:18:30.799 --> 00:18:32.870
every stalk was heavy laden. There

00:18:32.880 --> 00:18:36.070
wasn't a green leaf on a stalk because

00:18:36.080 --> 00:18:38.150
it was all taken up with cotton. And

00:18:38.160 --> 00:18:42.549
that means a tremendous harvest.

00:18:42.559 --> 00:18:46.789
A tremendous harvest.

00:18:46.799 --> 00:18:49.909
And I saw it in every direction. And I

00:18:49.919 --> 00:18:52.390
wondered when the vision was over, for

00:18:52.400 --> 00:18:55.190
it was a vision.

00:18:55.200 --> 00:18:58.230
I wondered because preachers normally

00:18:58.240 --> 00:19:02.950
use a wheat field to describe

00:19:02.960 --> 00:19:05.029
the harvest,

00:19:05.039 --> 00:19:07.110
but it was fields of cotton. But then I

00:19:07.120 --> 00:19:10.789
remembered the word that John

00:19:10.799 --> 00:19:14.070
wrote, "The fields are white unto

00:19:14.080 --> 00:19:18.870
harvest and the laborers are

00:19:18.870 --> 00:19:18.880
few."Think

00:19:18.880 --> 00:19:22.150
about that. The fields are white

00:19:22.160 --> 00:19:26.390
unto harvest. And I looked in every

00:19:26.400 --> 00:19:30.070
direction: north, south, east, and west.

00:19:30.080 --> 00:19:32.710
As far over the horizon as I could

00:19:32.720 --> 00:19:34.310
see, it was nothing but fields of

00:19:34.320 --> 00:19:37.590
cotton. I saw in the distance a couple

00:19:37.600 --> 00:19:40.630
of mechanical pickers.

00:19:40.640 --> 00:19:43.510
And then I saw to my left, which was the

00:19:43.520 --> 00:19:45.270
east,

00:19:45.280 --> 00:19:48.150
the most horrendous storm that was

00:19:48.160 --> 00:19:51.590
boiling up. The clouds were blacker than

00:19:51.600 --> 00:19:53.909
I'd ever seen in my

00:19:53.919 --> 00:19:57.350
life. The jagged forks of lightning were

00:19:57.360 --> 00:20:00.870
cutting across. And I knew if this

00:20:00.880 --> 00:20:04.549
harvest was not gathered, it was going

00:20:04.559 --> 00:20:08.390
to be destroyed. That storm,

00:20:08.400 --> 00:20:11.270
which I look back now and know was

00:20:11.280 --> 00:20:13.669
the great tribulation that's coming on

00:20:13.679 --> 00:20:16.549
this world,

00:20:16.559 --> 00:20:21.590
will destroy if it's not gathered.

00:20:21.600 --> 00:20:24.789
And then, for the first time, the Lord

00:20:24.799 --> 00:20:27.510
spoke to me

00:20:27.520 --> 00:20:31.110
in that vision and said,

00:20:34.240 --> 00:20:37.750
"I have called others

00:20:37.760 --> 00:20:41.590
for localities around the world,

00:20:41.600 --> 00:20:45.270
but I have called this ministry alone

00:20:45.280 --> 00:20:48.789
for the entirety of the

00:20:48.789 --> 00:20:48.799
world."I

00:20:48.799 --> 00:20:50.470
want to say that again. And I wouldn't

00:20:50.480 --> 00:20:53.110
say it for a long time because I thought

00:20:53.120 --> 00:20:56.789
it sounded self-serving,

00:20:56.799 --> 00:21:00.789
but I felt the Lord told me, "Yes, say

00:21:00.789 --> 00:21:00.799
it."He

00:21:00.799 --> 00:21:04.789
said, "I have called

00:21:04.799 --> 00:21:08.070
particular ministries for localities in

00:21:08.080 --> 00:21:10.950
certain parts of the world,

00:21:10.960 --> 00:21:14.230
but I have called this ministry alone

00:21:14.240 --> 00:21:17.110
for the entirety of the planet."Now, in

00:21:17.120 --> 00:21:20.870
a sense, every believer is called

00:21:20.880 --> 00:21:24.549
for the entirety of the world.

00:21:24.559 --> 00:21:28.870
But God has called this ministry to lead

00:21:28.880 --> 00:21:31.029
the

00:21:31.029 --> 00:21:31.039
way—to

00:21:31.039 --> 00:21:33.909
lead the way, the thousands and

00:21:33.919 --> 00:21:37.029
thousands of you who support this work.

00:21:37.039 --> 00:21:38.549
Well, that was basically the prophetic

00:21:38.559 --> 00:21:40.870
word on that one. But I want you to go

00:21:40.880 --> 00:21:42.870
back with me to whenever I told you I was

00:21:42.880 --> 00:21:46.230
in the spirit, and every single

00:21:46.240 --> 00:21:49.110
time I see towards the east, I see

00:21:49.120 --> 00:21:51.190
there's a storm. It looks like this:

00:21:51.200 --> 00:21:54.630
it's a massive hurricane, and

00:21:54.640 --> 00:21:56.230
every single time the Lord tells me,

00:21:56.240 --> 00:21:57.590
"Brandon, this is the spirit of

00:21:57.600 --> 00:21:59.909
the antichrist."And every single

00:21:59.919 --> 00:22:01.430
time, it's always toward the east

00:22:01.440 --> 00:22:03.110
whenever I'm looking in the spirit and I

00:22:03.120 --> 00:22:04.630
can see it. And he said,

00:22:04.640 --> 00:22:07.990
"Brandon, the last time I saw it, I

00:22:08.000 --> 00:22:10.789
could see and feel the raindrops coming.

00:22:10.799 --> 00:22:12.630
I could feel the raindrops of

00:22:12.630 --> 00:22:12.640
it."He

00:22:12.640 --> 00:22:15.430
said, "It's no longer on the distant

00:22:15.440 --> 00:22:16.789
shore.

00:22:16.799 --> 00:22:17.510
It's here.

00:22:17.510 --> 00:22:17.520
It's

00:22:17.520 --> 00:22:19.029
here.

00:22:19.039 --> 00:22:21.590
The end of the end is here."And the

00:22:21.600 --> 00:22:23.990
rain was coming down from this

00:22:24.000 --> 00:22:26.149
storm. It was just starting to

00:22:26.159 --> 00:22:28.390
come. The first bands were just starting

00:22:28.400 --> 00:22:30.310
to come upon the shore on the eastern

00:22:30.320 --> 00:22:32.070
seaside

00:22:32.070 --> 00:22:32.080
seaboard,

00:22:32.080 --> 00:22:34.630
right? The

00:22:34.640 --> 00:22:35.270
seashore.

00:22:35.760 --> 00:22:37.990
And it was coming. It was coming. I

00:22:38.000 --> 00:22:39.750
could see it, and the Lord told

00:22:39.760 --> 00:22:42.310
me, "You don't realize how close I

00:22:42.320 --> 00:22:44.870
am to my Son's

00:22:44.870 --> 00:22:44.880
return."People,

00:22:44.880 --> 00:22:46.549
