before, they're drinking their little

01:12:13.360 --> 01:12:15.110
cup, but the Lord said, 'It's time to go

01:12:15.120 --> 01:12:19.110
to the depth of the well.

01:12:19.120 --> 01:12:21.189
It's time to

01:12:24.719 --> 01:12:27.669
taste and see that the Lord

01:12:27.679 --> 01:12:30.950
is good

01:12:30.960 --> 01:12:33.750
in your life today.

01:12:33.760 --> 01:12:43.110
Taste and see that the Lord is good.

01:12:43.110 --> 01:12:43.120
He

01:12:43.120 --> 01:12:46.790
came to set the captives free,

01:12:46.800 --> 01:12:55.189
to bring sight to the blind,

01:12:55.199 --> 01:12:57.590
for his yoke is easy and his burden is

01:12:57.600 --> 01:13:02.630
light.

01:13:02.640 --> 01:13:04.870
Come unto me

01:13:04.880 --> 01:13:08.550
and I will give you rest.

01:13:08.560 --> 01:13:10.070
Take

01:13:10.080 --> 01:13:13.270
my yoke upon you.'We were singing that

01:13:13.280 --> 01:13:17.669
song two nights ago. 'I am weak

01:13:17.679 --> 01:13:20.149
and lonely

01:13:20.159 --> 01:13:28.310
and my burden's light.

01:13:28.320 --> 01:13:37.110
Take my yoke upon

01:13:37.110 --> 01:13:37.120
you.'Oh

01:13:37.120 --> 01:13:42.630
Father, come unto me.

01:13:42.640 --> 01:13:44.709
I feel his presence so strong right now.

01:13:49.199 --> 01:13:51.270
Glory to God that he wants to come and

01:13:51.280 --> 01:14:03.189
visit us.

01:14:03.199 --> 01:14:06.390
I just sit there.

01:14:06.400 --> 01:14:08.630
Father, I love you and we worship you

01:14:08.640 --> 01:14:14.870
today.

01:14:14.880 --> 01:14:18.070
He's so real to me.

01:14:18.080 --> 01:14:20.390
Most people

01:14:20.400 --> 01:14:22.790
I look at say the supernatural is

01:14:22.800 --> 01:14:28.310
more real to me than the natural.

01:14:28.320 --> 01:14:29.830
You say, 'Well, good for you,

01:14:29.830 --> 01:14:29.840
Brendan.'No,

01:14:29.840 --> 01:14:34.310
he wants to have that with you.

01:14:34.320 --> 01:14:38.070
You just have to sit at his feet.

01:14:38.080 --> 01:14:40.470
How hungry, how desperate, how bad do

01:14:40.480 --> 01:14:44.070
you want change in your life?

01:14:44.080 --> 01:14:45.590
Are you fed up with your

01:14:45.600 --> 01:14:49.189
circumstances?

01:14:49.199 --> 01:14:52.070
That's where he's at.

01:14:53.679 --> 01:14:56.229
At the place of surrender, of just

01:14:56.239 --> 01:14:58.149
selling out for Jesus. He told me, he said,

01:14:58.159 --> 01:15:00.709
'Brandon, I need more of

01:15:00.709 --> 01:15:00.719
you.'That's

01:15:00.719 --> 01:15:02.550
part of what I saw. I saw

01:15:02.560 --> 01:15:04.550
the beautiful purples in the

01:15:04.560 --> 01:15:07.590
trees. I see lavender. I could see the

01:15:07.600 --> 01:15:09.110
beautiful colors. And he was talking to

01:15:09.120 --> 01:15:12.229
me about the end times. And it sounds so

01:15:12.239 --> 01:15:15.110
out there, but I was looking at the

01:15:15.120 --> 01:15:17.189
beautiful trees and I was looking in the

01:15:17.199 --> 01:15:19.590
field the other day and I could

01:15:19.600 --> 01:15:21.110
see the purple and I could see the

01:15:21.120 --> 01:15:23.030
lavenders. I could see all the colors

01:15:23.040 --> 01:15:24.149
and he was talking about the

01:15:24.159 --> 01:15:26.149
supernatural

01:15:26.159 --> 01:15:27.990
and it's the way he talks to me, and

01:15:28.000 --> 01:15:32.550
he loves colors,

01:15:32.560 --> 01:15:36.229
fragrance.

01:15:36.239 --> 01:15:39.030
It's being intimate with him.

01:15:39.040 --> 01:15:42.149
Having an intimacy with God.

01:15:42.159 --> 01:15:45.030
I read George Washington Carver's

01:15:45.040 --> 01:15:48.630
book, The Man Who Talked to the Flowers.

01:15:48.640 --> 01:15:50.470
And I longed for that when he

01:15:50.480 --> 01:15:52.870
said, 'Dear

01:15:52.870 --> 01:15:52.880
Creator...'He

01:15:52.880 --> 01:15:55.189
talked to the peanut.

01:15:55.199 --> 01:15:56.950
And I thought, 'Lord, if you do that

01:15:56.960 --> 01:16:00.709
with him, you'll do it with me. You're

01:16:00.719 --> 01:16:03.189
no respecter of persons, but you are a

01:16:03.189 --> 01:16:03.199
respecter

01:16:03.199 --> 01:16:04.870
of faith and those that

01:16:04.880 --> 01:16:07.030
pursue you.

01:16:07.040 --> 01:16:10.630
How hard, how bad, how desperate are you

01:16:10.640 --> 01:16:13.910
for change in your life?'And so I set

01:16:13.920 --> 01:16:15.990
out to it and I said, 'Lord, I set out

01:16:16.000 --> 01:16:17.590
to do this.

01:16:19.679 --> 01:16:21.110
I'm going to fast something every other

01:16:21.110 --> 01:16:21.120
day.'And

01:16:21.120 --> 01:16:22.790
I set out for that for a

01:16:22.800 --> 01:16:27.350
long time. I did that for years

01:16:27.360 --> 01:16:30.070
seeking him. But I always

01:16:30.080 --> 01:16:31.510
keep the main thing the main thing.

01:16:31.520 --> 01:16:33.910
Keeping him first. All this stuff. It's

01:16:33.920 --> 01:16:35.830
not about works. Your

01:16:35.840 --> 01:16:38.149
self-righteousness is as filthy rags. No

01:16:38.159 --> 01:16:40.390
matter how much you try to impress

01:16:40.400 --> 01:16:42.390
him, you're never going to impress him.

01:16:42.400 --> 01:16:44.229
'Oh, you did it. Let me give you an

01:16:44.239 --> 01:16:48.149
applause.'No,

01:16:48.159 --> 01:16:50.630
it's all about him.

01:16:50.640 --> 01:16:54.229
It's his grace on my stinkiness.

01:16:54.239 --> 01:16:57.430
Thank you, Father, that you look past

01:16:57.440 --> 01:16:59.590
all of it by your blood when I take

01:16:59.600 --> 01:17:02.630
communion. No matter how messed up I

01:17:02.640 --> 01:17:05.189
come to you, just as I am without one

01:17:05.199 --> 01:17:08.390
plea, that blood was shed for me. Thank

01:17:08.400 --> 01:17:11.590
you, Lord. I pass all

01:17:11.600 --> 01:17:14.790
my issues and I come in by your

01:17:14.800 --> 01:17:16.310
blood.

01:17:16.320 --> 01:17:18.950
That's why I take communion

01:17:18.960 --> 01:17:21.110
all the time because I'm

01:17:21.120 --> 01:17:24.709
flawed. I'm messed up without it. And

01:17:24.719 --> 01:17:26.790
without his grace, without his blood, I

01:17:26.800 --> 01:17:29.189
say, 'Lord, I just want to be more. I

01:17:29.199 --> 01:17:30.950
want to come up higher. I want to

01:17:30.960 --> 01:17:33.590
sit on your floor. I

01:17:33.600 --> 01:17:35.030
mean, I don't care.'You know what I'm

01:17:35.040 --> 01:17:37.430
saying? 'I'll be the janitor up there

01:17:37.440 --> 01:17:38.950
next to you, Lord. Whatever it has to

01:17:38.960 --> 01:17:42.390
be, I just want to sit with you a while.

01:17:42.400 --> 01:17:44.550
If I could just sit with you a

01:17:44.560 --> 01:17:46.950
while for that one touch, that one

01:17:46.950 --> 01:17:46.960
moment.'That's

01:17:46.960 --> 01:17:48.630
why I go to Billy Burke

01:17:48.640 --> 01:17:50.870
meetings. When the presence of the Lord

01:17:50.880 --> 01:17:55.270
shows up, it changes your life forever.

01:17:55.280 --> 01:17:57.110
And then when you

01:17:57.110 --> 01:17:57.120
sow

01:17:57.120 --> 01:18:00.149
into something like that

01:18:00.159 --> 01:18:01.910
financially, whatever, I go, 'My

01:18:01.920 --> 01:18:03.430
goodness, if I could just give the shirt

01:18:03.440 --> 01:18:05.189
off my back to help it because

01:18:05.199 --> 01:18:07.350
it's

01:18:07.350 --> 01:18:07.360
beautiful.'It's

01:18:07.360 --> 01:18:11.750
not them,

01:18:11.760 --> 01:18:14.630
it's him. When you recognize

01:18:14.640 --> 01:18:16.709
authentic, when you get around

01:18:16.719 --> 01:18:18.950
authentic... Many people are just looking

01:18:18.960 --> 01:18:21.510
for authentic there. You go to church

01:18:21.520 --> 01:18:23.590
and you listen to all the

01:18:23.600 --> 01:18:26.070
stuff and you go, 'Where are you

01:18:26.080 --> 01:18:29.270
at in the midst of any of this?

01:18:29.280 --> 01:18:31.270
You're a thousand miles away,'as it feels

01:18:31.280 --> 01:18:34.790
like. But whenever you just sit with him

01:18:34.800 --> 01:18:38.470
a while, that one time, that one

01:18:38.480 --> 01:18:41.990
experience changes you forever.

01:18:42.000 --> 01:18:45.510
We had a friend, she

01:18:45.520 --> 01:18:49.350
emailed Diana, and she went to the

01:18:49.360 --> 01:18:50.390
Billy Burke meeting.

01:18:51.440 --> 01:18:53.110
And she had a problem with her

01:18:53.120 --> 01:18:54.149
esophagus.

01:18:54.159 --> 01:18:55.350
And

01:18:55.360 --> 01:18:57.430
she couldn't swallow and all

01:18:57.440 --> 01:18:59.590
these things. Well, she was

01:18:59.600 --> 01:19:01.110
overcoming big time like having to go to

01:19:01.120 --> 01:19:02.229
the doctor all the time and go under

01:19:02.239 --> 01:19:04.229
anesthesia and get her

01:19:04.239 --> 01:19:05.910
throat stretched.

01:19:05.920 --> 01:19:09.189
So she went to the Billy Burke meeting

01:19:09.199 --> 01:19:11.510
from a long ways, but she came so late

01:19:11.520 --> 01:19:13.430
because the traffic was so bad and she

01:19:13.440 --> 01:19:15.110
thought, 'If I could just have that one

01:19:15.120 --> 01:19:18.149
touch for one second, that one second

01:19:18.159 --> 01:19:20.950
from Jesus, that's all I

01:19:20.950 --> 01:19:20.960
need.'And

01:19:20.960 --> 01:19:22.550
that's why she kept coming even when she

01:19:22.560 --> 01:19:25.270
was so late. Well, she went to the

01:19:25.280 --> 01:19:27.110
meeting,

01:19:27.120 --> 01:19:29.030
and the spirit of the Lord

01:19:29.040 --> 01:19:31.350
spoke to Billy, I guess, and

01:19:31.360 --> 01:19:34.630
of course, he called her out,

01:19:34.640 --> 01:19:36.709
not even knowing her circumstance, and

01:19:36.719 --> 01:19:38.310
prayed over her, prophesied over her,

01:19:38.320 --> 01:19:40.550
and she was miraculously healed

01:19:40.560 --> 01:19:43.030
by the power of God.

01:19:43.040 --> 01:19:45.510
Out of all these times

01:19:45.520 --> 01:19:47.669
you suffer with something for so long,

01:19:47.679 --> 01:19:51.110
there's an expiration date to it.

01:19:51.120 --> 01:19:53.030
I just believe if we can just get

01:19:53.040 --> 01:19:55.590
underneath the glory

01:19:55.600 --> 01:19:58.870
and sit with him a while

01:19:58.880 --> 01:20:02.070
every single day, it's the glory from

01:20:02.080 --> 01:20:04.390
glory to glory who's changing you. And

01:20:04.400 --> 01:20:07.750
without that touch, without that

01:20:07.760 --> 01:20:10.790
visitation, we're never going to get the

01:20:10.800 --> 01:20:12.790
yoke and burden removed,

01:20:12.790 --> 01:20:12.800
yoke-destroying

01:20:12.800 --> 01:20:14.470
power out of those—that's what sets

01:20:14.480 --> 01:20:16.310
us free. But it's that burden on you,

01:20:16.310 --> 01:20:16.320
the

01:20:16.320 --> 01:20:17.910
things that are holding you down,

01:20:17.920 --> 01:20:19.910
that you have to have the glory

01:20:19.920 --> 01:20:22.790
to get... He came to set the captives

01:20:22.800 --> 01:20:24.709
free.

01:20:24.719 --> 01:20:26.790
And that's why I want to bring

01:20:26.800 --> 01:20:29.110
you to a place every time we do these

01:20:29.120 --> 01:20:32.470
videos, and I try to tap into that river

01:20:32.480 --> 01:20:34.630
because I know that it can go through

01:20:34.640 --> 01:20:36.550
this camera and visit you right

01:20:36.560 --> 01:20:39.350
where you are, even in a livestream,

01:20:39.350 --> 01:20:39.360
and

01:20:39.360 --> 01:20:41.750
you may be down, ready to end

01:20:41.760 --> 01:20:44.149
it all, and you just get a glimmer of

01:20:44.159 --> 01:20:46.310
hope, going, "Man, what is this

01:20:46.310 --> 01:20:46.320
guy

01:20:46.320 --> 01:20:48.550
talking about?"because I believe in it

01:20:48.560 --> 01:20:51.189
that much,

01:20:51.199 --> 01:20:53.990
because it's happened to me.

01:20:54.000 --> 01:20:56.630
I was so down and I was so broken, and

01:20:56.640 --> 01:20:59.430
there was a man named Ronald, and he was

01:20:59.440 --> 01:21:00.950
a missionary, and he came when I was ready

01:21:00.960 --> 01:21:04.390
to end it all, ready to go off a bridge,

01:21:04.400 --> 01:21:06.229
and I thought, "If I don't get a touch

01:21:06.229 --> 01:21:06.239
today..."because

01:21:06.239 --> 01:21:09.189
I'm so desperate for it

01:21:09.199 --> 01:21:12.390
because of how dark my circumstances

01:21:12.390 --> 01:21:12.400
were,

01:21:12.400 --> 01:21:14.950
that there's nothing else to live for. "I

01:21:14.960 --> 01:21:17.910
need a touch from Jesus."So, I went to

01:21:17.920 --> 01:21:20.630
this church in Crescent, Oklahoma,

01:21:20.640 --> 01:21:24.149
and the man of God called me

01:21:24.159 --> 01:21:26.149
out,

01:21:26.159 --> 01:21:30.070
and it gave me hope.

01:21:30.080 --> 01:21:32.070
And I know I've told this story

01:21:32.080 --> 01:21:34.550
before, but I just feel there's somebody

01:21:34.560 --> 01:21:38.950
tonight that is believing for hope.

01:21:38.960 --> 01:21:41.110
And Jesus wants to meet you right where

01:21:41.120 --> 01:21:43.189
you are, even in your house, your car,

01:21:43.199 --> 01:21:45.189
your living room, wherever you might be,

01:21:45.199 --> 01:21:46.630
in your bedroom, wherever you're

01:21:46.640 --> 01:21:48.870
watching this. And Jesus wants to meet

01:21:48.880 --> 01:21:52.070
you right at the point of your need.

01:21:52.080 --> 01:21:54.629
He loves you, and he has died for you,

01:21:54.639 --> 01:21:56.550
and he rose again on the third day. He

01:21:56.560 --> 01:21:58.310
suffered and he died that you might live

01:21:58.320 --> 01:22:03.110
in victory today.

01:22:03.120 --> 01:22:05.590
But all you have to do is reach out to

01:22:05.600 --> 01:22:07.189
him, like the woman with the issue of

01:22:07.199 --> 01:22:11.350
blood. She spent all she had,

01:22:11.360 --> 01:22:15.110
but she grew worse, but she

01:22:15.120 --> 01:22:18.070
said to herself, "If I can touch but his

01:22:18.070 --> 01:22:18.080
hem,

01:22:18.080 --> 01:22:21.430
I can be

01:22:21.430 --> 01:22:21.440
whole."Jesus

01:22:21.440 --> 01:22:23.990
Christ, the same yesterday, today,

01:22:24.000 --> 01:22:27.350
and forever. And if he would allow that

01:22:27.360 --> 01:22:29.590
to happen back then, and it happened for

01:22:29.600 --> 01:22:32.310
her, he'll do it again,

01:22:32.320 --> 01:22:35.590
and he'll do it again, and he'll do it

01:22:35.600 --> 01:22:39.189
again. He is no respecter of persons if

01:22:39.199 --> 01:22:41.830
you just reach out by faith and grab a

01:22:41.840 --> 01:22:43.350
hold of that hem of his garment and

01:22:43.360 --> 01:22:45.030
say, "Lord,

01:22:45.040 --> 01:22:49.110
I am here and I need a touch from you

01:22:49.120 --> 01:22:55.669
today. I'm desperate for it.

01:22:55.679 --> 01:22:59.189
I can't keep going on this way.

01:22:59.199 --> 01:23:03.750
I can't keep living like

01:23:03.750 --> 01:23:03.760
this."Father,

01:23:03.760 --> 01:23:06.709
I thank you, Lord, that you're

01:23:06.719 --> 01:23:08.550
meeting them right now at the point of

01:23:08.560 --> 01:23:11.669
their need, that every single person

01:23:11.679 --> 01:23:14.629
who's here that needs hope, you're their

01:23:14.639 --> 01:23:17.430
hope, that you've come to set the

01:23:17.440 --> 01:23:19.830
captives free tonight.

01:23:19.840 --> 01:23:21.990
And Father, I thank you, Lord, that

01:23:22.000 --> 01:23:24.149
peace that passes all understanding is

01:23:24.159 --> 01:23:26.470
flooding their house, flooding their

01:23:26.480 --> 01:23:28.470
car, wherever they are

01:23:28.480 --> 01:23:31.110
watching this. The peace that passes all

01:23:31.120 --> 01:23:33.270
understanding is ministering to them

01:23:33.280 --> 01:23:35.430
right now today,

01:23:35.440 --> 01:23:38.709
giving them a fresh and

01:23:38.709 --> 01:23:38.719
anew.

01:23:38.719 --> 01:23:40.070
Father, I thank you, Lord, that

01:23:40.080 --> 01:23:41.830
nothing's too big and nothing's too

01:23:41.840 --> 01:23:47.990
small. Jesus paid the price for it all.

01:23:48.000 --> 01:23:49.830
Father, we love you, Lord, and we lift

01:23:49.840 --> 01:23:51.830
up all our

01:23:51.830 --> 01:23:51.840
circumstances,

01:23:51.840 --> 01:23:53.990
all our needs, and you

01:23:54.000 --> 01:23:56.470
said you supply all of them, and we give

01:23:56.480 --> 01:23:58.149
you all the glory for that right now.

01:23:58.159 --> 01:24:00.229
Now, you may be watching this today and

01:24:00.239 --> 01:24:02.790
you say, "Brandon, I don't even—I'm not

01:24:02.800 --> 01:24:05.270
even a born-again Christian. I don't

01:24:05.280 --> 01:24:07.350
even know Jesus. But I watch this and

01:24:07.360 --> 01:24:09.590
it sounds awesome, and I'm so broken and

01:24:09.600 --> 01:24:12.629
I'm so burned out, and I'm on drugs. I'm

01:24:12.639 --> 01:24:15.030
strung out on pornography.

01:24:15.040 --> 01:24:16.950
My wife and I are fighting all the time.

01:24:16.960 --> 01:24:19.590
Whatever it may be. I drink a

01:24:19.590 --> 01:24:19.600
six-pack

01:24:19.600 --> 01:24:21.750
of beer every couple of hours or

01:24:21.760 --> 01:24:24.390
whatever, I don't know, and I'm at

01:24:24.400 --> 01:24:27.590
the end of my rope, but I want Jesus

01:24:27.600 --> 01:24:29.669
Christ to be my Lord and personal Savior

01:24:29.679 --> 01:24:32.390
today. Could you please help

01:24:32.390 --> 01:24:32.400
me?"You

01:24:32.400 --> 01:24:34.870
came to the right place.

01:24:34.880 --> 01:24:36.790
We want to say a prayer right with you

01:24:36.800 --> 01:24:38.950
right now, and we want to lead you in.

01:24:38.960 --> 01:24:40.950
It's called the sinner's prayer, and you

01:24:40.960 --> 01:24:43.189
say this and you accept Jesus Christ as

01:24:43.199 --> 01:24:45.189
your Lord and personal Savior. Because

01:24:45.199 --> 01:24:47.270
I'm telling you, you came here not by

01:24:47.280 --> 01:24:49.030
coincidence, but because God had a

01:24:49.040 --> 01:24:51.430
purpose for your life tonight. And he's

01:24:51.440 --> 01:24:53.590
wanting to—he's out there and

01:24:53.600 --> 01:24:55.669
he's extending his lifeline to you,

01:24:55.679 --> 01:24:59.590
saying, "Will you accept me today?

01:24:59.600 --> 01:25:02.310
Will you surrender yourself to me today

01:25:02.320 --> 01:25:05.350
and let me take care of it?

01:25:05.360 --> 01:25:08.310
You can't do it, but I can."He says,

01:25:08.320 --> 01:25:11.270
